name: Focus Through
description:
A snowy pine branch illuminated by the sun as viewed between two cedar trunks.

The depth of field is altered, but the position in space remains unchanged, allowing the viewer to see past the visual obstacle.

Photographed 2017. GIF Created 2021.

Photographed in situ, without the use of artificial lighting or staging. Photoshop only used for resizing and GIF building.

1024x685 GIF

Winter GIF Series: 1/3
